          <p>Subconscious patterns that influence habits, identity, and relationship with the body.</p>
          <p class="price">$197</p>
          <a href="/products" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card featured-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
